Package: GMHmicrobiome
Type: Package
Title: Functions to support microbiome data analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Martin","Mortensen", "martin@mortensen.one", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: This package contains functions to support analyses of 
